name: IPLookup
0:
”Alexa, ask eye pee lookup where is four dot four dot four dot four”
”Alexa, ask eye pee lookup who is four dot four dot four dot four?”
”Alexa, ask eye pee lookup and lookup four dot four dot four dot four”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: eye pee lookup
des: This looks up the location of a given ip4 address. Make sure to spell out the IP address with four numbers separated by the word 'dot.' - So you might ask for "four dot four dot four dot four."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
